theorem Topology.interior_closure_interior_closure_eq
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · -- `interior (closure (interior (closure A))) ⊆ interior (closure A)`
    have hsubset : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      have : (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
      exact closure_mono this
    exact interior_mono hsubset
  · -- `interior (closure A) ⊆ interior (closure (interior (closure A)))`
    have hsubset : (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆
        closure (interior (closure A)) := subset_closure
    have h_open : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
    exact interior_maximal hsubset h_open

import Mathlib

namespace Topology

variable {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]

def P1 (A : Set X) : Prop :=
  A ⊆ closure (interior A)

theorem Topology.interiorClosure_satisfies_P1 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P1 (interior (closure A)) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P1]
  simpa using
    (subset_closure :
      (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)))

theorem Topology.clopen_of_isClosed_and_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA_closed : IsClosed A) (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) :
    IsOpen A ∧ IsClosed A := by
  have h_open : IsOpen A :=
    (Topology.P3_iff_isOpen_of_isClosed (X := X) (A := A) hA_closed).1 hP3
  exact ⟨h_open, hA_closed⟩
